1. Ja *igram* fudbal sa drugovima svaki vikend. (I play football with my friends every weekend.)
2. Oni *igraju* šah već satima. (They have been playing chess for hours.)
3. Da li biste *igrali* društvene igre sa mnom? (Would you like to play board games with me?)
4. Mi *igramo* košarku u parku svakog popodneva. (We play basketball in the park every afternoon.)
5. Deca *igraju* se u dvorištu. (The children are playing in the yard.)
6. Da li si *igrao* ovu igru pre? (Have you played this game before?)
7. Oni će *igrati* koncert u subotu. (They will play a concert on Saturday.)
8. Moja sestra *igra* klavir već 10 godina. (My sister has been playing the piano for 10 years.)
9. *Igrajući* video igre, izgubio sam osećaj za vreme. (Playing video games, I lost track of time.)
10. Nakon ručka, deca su *počela da igraju* igru skrivača. (After lunch, the kids started playing hide-and-seek.)